DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to configure a resilience pipeline with chaos engineering strategies using Simmy. The example shows how to add fault injection (2% rate), latency injection (50% of remaining requests), outcome injection (10% of remaining requests), and behavior injection (1% of remaining requests) after regular resilience strategies.
