    DelayGenerator --> if_state_step3
    if_state_step3 --> GeneratedDelay: positive
    if_state_step3 --> NormalizedDelay: null or negative
    GeneratedDelay --> setNext
    NormalizedDelay --> setNext
    setNext --> [*]
