TITLE: Implementing a Custom Action Generator in Hedging Strategy
DESCRIPTION: Example of implementing a custom ActionGenerator for a hedging resilience pipeline. The generator creates specialized actions for each hedging attempt, with access to both primary and action contexts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/app-vnext/polly/blob/main/docs/strategies/hedging.md#2025-04-18_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: csharp
