TITLE: Anti-Pattern: Injecting Delay with Behavior Chaos in C#
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates an anti-pattern where a behavior strategy is incorrectly used to inject delays. This approach is not recommended.
SOURCE: https://github.com/app-vnext/polly/blob/main/docs/chaos/behavior.md#2025-04-18_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
var pipeline = new ResiliencePipelineBuilder()
    .AddChaosBehavior(new ChaosBehaviorStrategyOptions
    {
        BehaviorGenerator = static async args =>
        {
            await Task.Delay(TimeSpan.FromSeconds(7), args.Context.CancellationToken);
        }
    })
    .Build();
```

